---

<DocsLayout title="Components" description="Full inventory of Portefaix platform components organised by architecture layer.">
  <p class="doc-eyebrow">// reference / components</p>

  <h1>Platform Components</h1>

  <p>
    Portefaix assembles a curated set of CNCF and open-source components into a coherent,
    production-ready platform. Components are organised into seven architecture layers,
    each with a distinct operational concern.
  </p>

  <figure>
    <div style="position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;" onclick="document.getElementById('arch-modal').showModal()">
      <img
        src="/diagrams/portefaix-architecture-flat-v2.svg"
        alt="Portefaix Platform Architecture — seven layers: GitOps Foundation, Networking, Security, Observability, System & Data, Platform Tools, Chaos Engineering"
        style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; display: block;"
      />
      <span style="position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45); color: #fff; font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; pointer-events: none;">
        🔍 Click to zoom
      </span>
    </div>
    <figcaption style="text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      Portefaix Platform Architecture — 7 layers, 50+ components ·
      <a href="/diagrams/portefaix-architecture-flat-v2.svg" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: #2563eb;">View full size ↗</a>
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <dialog
    id="arch-modal"
    style="max-width: 95vw; max-height: 95vh; padding: 0; border: none; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); overflow: hidden; background: #fff;"
  >
    <div style="position: relative;">
      <img
        src="/diagrams/portefaix-architecture-flat-v2.svg"
        alt="Portefaix Platform Architecture — full size"
        style="width: 90vw; max-height: 90vh; object-fit: contain; display: block;"
      />
      <button
        onclick="document.getElementById('arch-modal').close()"
        aria-label="Close diagram"
        style="position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; border: none; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55); color: #fff; font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"
      >✕</button>
    </div>
  </dialog>

  <script>
    const modal = document.getElementById('arch-modal');
    modal?.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (e.target === modal) modal.close(); });
  </script>

  {layers.map((layer) => (
    <>
      <h2 style={`border-left: 4px solid ${layer.color}; padding-left: 0.75rem;`}>
        {layer.category}
      </h2>
      <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: -0.5rem;">{layer.description}</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Component</th>
            <th>Role</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {layer.items.map((item) => (
            <tr>
              <td>
                <a href={item.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>{item.name}</strong></a>
                {item.ebpf && (
                  <span style="margin-left: 0.4rem; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; background: #ffedd5; color: #c2410c; border: 1px solid #fdba74; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1px 5px;">eBPF</span>
                )}
              </td>
              <td>{item.role}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </>
  ))}

  <h2>CNCF Landscape Alignment</h2>

  <p>
    Portefaix deliberately chooses components from the
    <a href="https://landscape.cncf.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CNCF landscape</a>
    where possible, prioritising projects that are either CNCF Graduated or Incubating. This
    ensures long-term community support, security audits, and interoperability.
  </p>

  <div class="callout callout-info">
    <p>
      <strong>Versioning:</strong> Specific component versions and Helm chart versions are tracked
      in the <a href="https://github.com/portefaix/portefaix-hub" target="_blank" rel="noopener">portefaix-hub</a>
      repository and updated automatically via Renovate Bot.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
